description: This common Sakura purrs with a rating of 50, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 50, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Stringalong for East, 2 for South, and Leverage for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [50 Votes, Common]
